---
title: Easy Cheesy Beef & Pork Ragu Loaded Ciabattas with Baby Leaf and Carrot Ribbon Salad
description: Perfect for a midweek meal, these Easy Cheesy Beef & Pork Ragu Loaded Ciabattas can be on your table in less than 25 minutes. A quicker version of the Italian beef ragù or a sloppy joe, it's still full of flavour.
